dottir
======

A Rust reimplementation of Dotter (Sonnhammer & Durbin 1995), a sliding-window
sequence dot-matrix plotter.

Algorithm lineage
-----------------

The window-size estimation in `dottir-core::karlin` is a direct port of the
Karlin/Altschul statistics implementation in `dotterApp/dotterKarlin.c` of
seqtools-4.28 (https://github.com/douglasgscofield/seqtools-4.28), which in
turn descends from NCBI BLAST.

The sliding-window sum recurrence, anti-diagonal suppression rule, and pixel
max-merge logic in `dottir-core::sliding`, `::antidiag`, and `::pixel`
preserve the algorithms documented at `dotterApp/dotplot.c:1308`, `:1405`,
and surrounding lines.

